data.description: AMAZING move in ready home at an AMAZING price! Refrigerator, washer and dryer included! You'll be proud to call this 7 year young, upgraded, well maintained, immaculate maintenance free townhome yours. Nestled in the midst of gorgeous wooded surroundings with a private back yard patio area.  You'll adore the tranquility of living so close to historical Wake Forest yet minutes from downtown Raleigh. Enjoy a double driveway, one car garage, upgraded owner's suite bath and gorgeous kitchen with white cabinets, granite looking counters and beautiful laminate flooring throughout the 1st floor.
